Attachment upgrade tasks need to include some smarts to try and clean up attachment repositories that have been affected by some old attachment handling bugs (such as CONF-6073).

For example, for an attachment that has been clobbered by CONF-6073, we will have to kill the affected attachment record to avoid potential "attachment data not found" results

